<style> :root { --icon-size-large: 50px; --icon-size-medium: 45px; --icon-size-small: 35px; --icon-size-xsmall: 25px; --icon-size-xxsmall: 15px; --padding-left-large: 60px; --padding-left-medium: 55px; --padding-left-small: 45px; --padding-left-xsmall: 35px; --padding-left-xxsmall: 25px } .custom-list-item { align-items: center; background-position: 0; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: var(--icon-size-large); display: flex; height: 65px; list-style: none; margin-bottom: 10px; padding-left: var(--padding-left-large); transition: height .3s ease, background-size .3s ease } .custom-list-item.seguridad { background-image: url(Iconos/iconosrealissa/r10.webp) } .custom-list-item.naturaleza { background-image: url(Iconos/iconosrealissa/r12.webp) } .custom-list-item.educacion { background-image: url(Iconos/iconosrealissa/r15.webp) } .custom-list-item.casas { background-image: url(Iconos/iconosrealissa/r11.webp) } .custom-list-item.costo-vida { background-image: url(Iconos/iconosrealissa/r13.webp) } .custom-list-item.impuestos { background-image: url(Iconos/iconosrealissa/r16.webp) } .custom-list-item.salud { background-image: url(Iconos/iconosrealissa/r17.webp) } @media (max-width:1200px) { .custom-list-item { background-size: var(--icon-size-medium); height: 50px; padding-left: var(--padding-left-medium) } } @media (max-width:992px) { .custom-list-item { background-size: var(--icon-size-small); height: 40px; padding-left: var(--padding-left-small) } } @media (max-width:768px) { .custom-list-item { background-size: var(--icon-size-xsmall); height: 30px; padding-left: var(--padding-left-xsmall) } } @media (max-width:576px) { .custom-list-item { background-size: var(--icon-size-xxsmall); height: 20px; padding-left: var(--padding-left-xxsmall) } } ul li+p { margin-left: var(--padding-left-large); margin-top: 0 } @media (max-width:768px) { ul li+p { margin-left: var(--padding-left-xsmall) } } @media (max-width:576px) { ul li+p { margin-left: var(--padding-left-xxsmall) } } .numero { font-family: Franklin Gothic Medium, Arial Narrow, Arial, sans-serif } #mapa iframe { border: 0; height: 300px; transition: height .3s ease; width: 100% } @media (max-width:1200px) { #mapa iframe { height: 250px } } @media (max-width:992px) { #mapa iframe { height: 200px } } @media (max-width:768px) { #mapa iframe { height: 180px } } @media (max-width:576px) { #mapa iframe { height: 150px } }</style><div class="container mt-5"> <div class="row"> <!-- Primer Div --> <div class="col-md-5 mb-4 textoComponentes"> <h2 class="mb-4">Real Estate: Cape Coral, Florida.</h2> <ul class="list-unstyled"> <li>West Coast of Florida, on the Gulf of Mexico.</li> <li>Part of Lee County.</li> <li>Current population: <span class="numero">750,000</span> residents.</li> </ul> <h6 class="m-4"><strong>Nearby Points</strong></h6> <!-- Added 'list-unstyled' to remove bullets --> <ul class="list-unstyled"> <!-- Buttons to update the map --> <li><button class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 10px;" onclick="showMap('Fort')">Fort Myers <span class="numero">9</span> mi.</button></li> <li><button class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 10px;" onclick="showMap('Naples')">Naples <span class="numero">43</span> mi.</button></li> <li><button class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 10px;" onclick="showMap('Miami')">Miami <span class="numero">157</span> mi.</button></li> <li><button class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 10px;" onclick="showMap('Orlando')">Orlando <span class="numero">166</span> mi.</button></li> </ul> <div id="mapa" class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"> <!-- El iframe se actualizarÃ¡ con JavaScript --> <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d228225.33049094962!2d-82.16053479436344!3d26.647816818523545!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x88db44a7e78016f5%3A0xafd1a4163a9b6ff2!2sCape%20Coral%2C%20Florida%2C%20EE.%20UU.!5e0!3m2!1ses-419!2sar!4v1729277554645!5m2!1ses-419!2sar" width="100%" height="300" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe> </div> </div><!-- Second Div (Additional Space or Other Content) --> <div class="col-md-2 mb-4"> <!-- Additional space or other content here --></div><!-- Third Div --> <div class="col-md-5 mb-4 textoComponentes"> <h2 class="mb-4">Why Invest in Cape Coral</h2> <!-- Added 'list-unstyled' to remove bullets --> <ul> <li class="custom-list-item security"><strong>SECURITY</strong></li> <p>It has one of the lowest crime rates in the country.</p> <li class="custom-list-item nature"><strong>THE POWER OF NATURE</strong></li> <p>Developments are located by the water and nature. It has over <span class="numero">640</span> km of canals.</p> <li class="custom-list-item education"><strong>FREE AND QUALITY EDUCATION</strong></li> <p>The average and standards of education in institutions are high in training and quality. Additionally, there is broad freedom to send children to the public school of each family's choice.</p> <li class="custom-list-item single-family-homes"><strong>SINGLE-FAMILY HOMES</strong></li> <p>Most homes are single-family with no HOA / Monthly fees.</p> <li class="custom-list-item cost-of-living"><strong>LOWER COST OF LIVING</strong></li> <p>The cost of living in Cape Coral is <span class="numero">4</span>% lower than the national average.</p> <li class="custom-list-item taxes"><strong>FEWER TAXES</strong></li> <p>There is no state income tax.</p> <li class="custom-list-item health"><strong>HEALTH</strong></li> <p>The cost of health care is <span class="numero">5</span>% below the national average.</p> </ul> </div> </div>